        public Vet(java.lang.String n)
        Vet constructor post: randomPet, randomRoom, randomClient, randomDate, randomDrug, randomDetail and randomCH are created. ArrayClient, arrayDrug, arrayRoom and arrayClinicHistories are initialized. RandomClient is assigned to arrayClient. RandomPet and randomDrug are assigned to randomRoom.
